{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-js","path":"/posts/2017-10-20-fonts-and-style/","webpackCompilationHash":"a634b47fc7865b77ff3f","result":{"data":{"currentPost":{"html":"<p>글을 보기 좋게 만들자. 당장 사이트를 제일 많이 보는 사람은 나일테니 맥/iOS에서 잘 보이는 폰트를 우선 선택했다.</p>\n<h3>본문 글꼴</h3>\n<p>본문을 위한 글꼴은 <a href=\"http://www.chengyinliu.com/whatfont.html\">WhatFont Chrome Extension</a>을 이용해서 facebook의 폰트 설정을 가져왔다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\">body<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>h1<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> h2<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> h3<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> h4<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> h5<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> h6<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> blockquote\n  <span class=\"token property\">font-family</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"SF Optimized\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> -apple-system<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> system-ui<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\".SFNSText-Regular\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> sans-serif<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>코드 글꼴</h3>\n<p>코드를 위한 글꼴은 구글 검색으로 몇 가지 정보를 취합하여 설정했다.</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\">p<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span>pre.highlight<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> blockquote\n  code\n    <span class=\"token property\">font-family</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Menlo-Regular\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> <span class=\"token string\">\"Lucida Console\"</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> Monaco<span class=\"token punctuation\">,</span> monospace<span class=\"token punctuation\">;</span></code></pre></div>\n<h3>인용문 스타일</h3>\n<p>인용문을 잘 보이게 하는 스타일도 적용했다.</p>\n<blockquote>\n<p>인용문은 이렇게 보인다.</p>\n</blockquote>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"css\"><pre class=\"language-css\"><code class=\"language-css\">blockquote\n  <span class=\"token property\">background</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> #f9f9f9\n  <span class=\"token property\">border-left</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 10px solid #ccc\n  <span class=\"token property\">margin</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0px\n  <span class=\"token property\">padding</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> 0.5em 10px</code></pre></div>\n<ul>\n<li>참고: <a href=\"https://css-tricks.com/snippets/css/simple-and-nice-blockquote-styling/\">Simple and Nice Blockquote Styling</a></li>\n</ul>","frontmatter":{"title":"글꼴과 스타일 설정","date":"2017-10-20","tags":["housekeeping"]},"timeToRead":1},"nextPost":{"frontmatter":{"title":"MathJax 설정"},"fields":{"slug":"/posts/2017-11-07-with-mathjax/"}},"previousPost":{"frontmatter":{"title":"뷰포트 설정"},"fields":{"slug":"/posts/2017-10-19-view-port/"}}},"pageContext":{"isCreatedByStatefulCreatePages":false,"slug":"/posts/2017-10-20-fonts-and-style/","nextSlug":"/posts/2017-11-07-with-mathjax/","previousSlug":"/posts/2017-10-19-view-port/"}}}